Even for base conversion bigger than 10, it is tricky because we have to check if the key is greater than 9. If it is, we need to replace it by the corresponding letter in alphabet.

$a=array_reverse(array_unique(str_split($s)));
foreach($a as $k=>$v) {
        $h[strtoupper(base_convert($k,10,36))]=$v;
}
